collections.name: Greedy Goblins 20 (Eth)
collections.description:
These are the greediest of goblins! Each unique Greedy Goblin comes with a unique name, style, & background!
  These goblins live in the mountains in a land called Erondale (A'-ron-dale). Inside this land are humans, orcs, dwarves, elves, & of course, the greedy little goblins! (Little; except for the soldier goblins).
 The Goblins are notoriously lazy creatures; slobbish even! They hate to work for their bit; & so it is; they are in constant conflict with the other inhabitants of Erondale!
* This is Kattiña (cat-teen-yah). She is the Royal Princess Goblin of King Bágwárt!
* She is a mix of elf & goblin; she is the only goblin with light colored skin, instead of the traditional greens, purples & black!
* Being an elf makes Kattiña exceptionally fast & quiet; therefore, all cards paired under her command gain SPEED +50%; & STAMINA (or distance traveled) +25%. Her bonuses apply to every card in her command!
* Greedy Goblin Character cards; (over 50+ goblin cards in the starting deck); are all designed to be special cards!
Special Goblins can be played in combination with other 'Specials' to create unique strategies! When paired with Common Goblin cards they can build much larger raiding parties!
* The Bágwárts have been perfecting white magic & healing for over 800 years; while King Squibnärd practices the art of dark magic & reviving the dead!
* Kattiña is able to practice some dark magic since she is half night elf & half Goblin! She is also a healer & gains double the healing bonus of a Royal Goblin!
* All Royal Greedy Goblins gain an advantage of 25% in speed, power, & defense; this also applies to any Goblins paired w/ Royal Goblins!
* Greedy Goblins conduct many raids on the neighboring villages; & even OTHER goblins...they are insatiable, GREEDY Goblins!
* There are over 50+ Greedy Goblins in this exclusive collection! From commoners, to soldiers, politicians, diplomats, & the rarest; the royal goblins!
* These Greedy Goblins were designed to be integrated into a digital nft fard game; future launch to be announced at my X page @AlphaDoge12🐦 Thanks for supporting my art! Lots to come; BitSwagger aka Anthony, https://rarible.com/bitswagger, & OpenSea

collections.name: Crypto Outlaws
collections.description:
Welcome to Crypto Outlaws, a unique collection of NFTs that delves into the shadowy and intriguing underworld of cryptocurrencies. Each character is inspired by a crypto villain, creating an exclusive gallery of figures that represent the most mysterious and audacious side of the digital world.

The Collection
Each character in the Crypto Outlaws collection is completely unique and has been meticulously designed, reflecting the persona of a criminal from the world of cryptocurrencies. From hackers to money launderers, these characters are a blend of intriguing, powerful, and mysterious figures. They each have their own stories and are part of a network of distinct characters with futuristic accessories and traits that evoke the rebellion and audacity of the crypto world.

The Philosophy
Here, we’re not just collecting digital art. We’re collecting stories. Each purchase of a Crypto Outlaws NFT grants you access to an exclusive and rare photo related to the theme of money laundering — a tribute to the mysterious and enigmatic methods that exist in the financial underworld. These photos are unique, real-life images that serve as a “passport” into the secretive world of digital finance, always respecting the ethics of digital art and the security of transactions.

What Awaits You
Exclusive Characters: Each NFT is a one-of-a-kind piece of art, with a distinct and unmistakable villain.
Hidden Stories: Each purchase unlocks a piece of the narrative, revealing the secrets of the crypto world.
Rare Photos: Upon purchase, receive a true and rare photo linked to the theme of money laundering — an additional valuable piece of art and culture to enhance your collection.
The Digital Revolution
"Crypto Outlaws" is not just about digital art — it’s about challenging conventions and entering a new world of collecting. The cryptocurrency market is the ideal backdrop for these antiheroes, and with this collection, we bring to light a new era of NFTs that blends art, culture, and the shadow of illicit transactions.

Join us on this digital journey and own your Crypto Outlaw. After all, in the world of crypto, no one is truly innocent.

collections.name: Hushies Snapshot
collections.description: Hushies Snapshot are a collection of 5,000 pixel art aliens called Hushies. These aliens became extremely bored one day and decided to find the planet that had the most intelligent lifeforms in the universe, which Earth, somehow. Some Hushies descended upon Earth because they liked humankind and wanted to help bring order and spirituality to our society. They helped create structures like the Pyramids of Giza, Machu Picchu, and Stonehenge. Other Hushies just wanted to mess with us and created things like Crop Circles to confuse us or Area 51 to watch over us. As humans evolved and became more chaotic, Hushies decided to spend less time on Earth and are often in their Mothership, where their collective knowledge is stored. Occasionally, Hushies can be spotted hovering around the world, typically near the structures they helped create.

collections.name: Tony's Digital Art Collection No. 1
collections.description: I enjoy creating digital art work that tells a story. I do not restrict myself to creating any particular art style or subject matter.   I produce what I like and my imagination is key to conjuring up interesting digital art pieces. If others like my art work, then that is a big plus for me. My past experience in producing photographic images has provided me with a visual art awareness and understanding together with the ability to produce digital images using computer software, assisted by AI. My collection is a mixture of subject matter and image types. It is a pleasure to share my art work with others and to afford them the opportunity of acquiring a piece of art work that they particularly like and will treasure.
